title: Spacious 1 BR at The Princeton Hall Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '888 Grand Ave - 102 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Spacious 1 BR at The Princeton Hall Apartments', 'The apartment has a ton of historic character from the 1920s, which makes it very charming and comfortable.', 'The apartment features hardwood floors throughout, new energy-efficient windows, updated lighting fixtures, and vintage tile in the bathroom.', 'The kitchen features original built-in cabinetry with stainless steel appliances.', 'Located in the exciting Victoria Crossing stretch of Grand Avenue, the Princeton Hall is the perfect place for anyone who wants to experience the best of Grand Ave living!', "With a fantastic location, you can walk out your front door and be within blocks of restaurants such as Salut, Axel's Bonfire, and Caffe Latte.", 'You could also choose to do some shopping at one of the original shops on Grand Avenue or take a walk down the longest stretch of Victorian homes in America on Summit Avenue.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Separate Kitchen and Dining', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Nine Foot Ceilings', '24/7 Emergency Maintenance', 'Renovated Laundry Room', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', 'Convenient Coinless Laundry', 'Access to Fitness Center & Community Room', 'Heat and Water Paid', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 750', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,024.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
